Dick Wesson (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dick_Wesson_(actor) 0 Richard Lewis "Dick" Wesson (November 19, 1922 – April 25, 1996) was a prolific character actor, comedian, comedy writer, and producer. The dark haired man with a flat top haircut was frequently confused with announcer Dick Wesson.
